          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1657005964205-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot with the bulgur wheat to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped shallot </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Once starting to soften, add your <strong>ground allspice </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for a further 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, stir through the <strong>cooked bulgur </strong>until fully combined</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
