          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>diced tomatoes </strong>to a bowl with your<strong> ground sumac</strong>, <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– these are your <strong>sumac tomatoes</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1657005970346-x200.jpg",
